<item>
            <title>[SUREFIRE-1795] surefire-reports is not working in parallel</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-1795</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Create a maven project, add 4 testng classes to print out logs, for example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;package&lt;/span&gt; com.verizon.rngverify;

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; org.testng.annotations.Test;

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;testClass1 {  
    @Test &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; void test1() &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; Exception { 
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;.out.println(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;class1method1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;); 
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Thread&lt;/span&gt;.sleep(100); 
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;System&lt;/span&gt;.out.println(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;class1method1 end&quot;&lt;/span&gt;); 
    }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Create a testng xml file to control above 4 test cases in parallel with 4 threads:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&amp;lt;suite name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;tsname&quot;&lt;/span&gt; parallel=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;tests&quot;&lt;/span&gt; thread-count=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;4&quot;&lt;/span&gt; verbose=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
  &amp;lt;test name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;testname1_in_xml&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;classes&amp;gt; 
      &amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;com.verizon.rngverify.testClass1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;/classes&amp;gt; 
  &amp;lt;/test&amp;gt;  
  
  &amp;lt;test name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;testname2_in_xml&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;classes&amp;gt; 
      &amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;com.verizon.rngverify.testClass2&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;/classes&amp;gt; 
  &amp;lt;/test&amp;gt;  

  &amp;lt;test name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;testname3_in_xml&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;classes&amp;gt; 
      &amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;com.verizon.rngverify.testClass3&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;/classes&amp;gt; 
  &amp;lt;/test&amp;gt;  

  &amp;lt;test name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;testname4_in_xml&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;classes&amp;gt; 
      &amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;com.verizon.rngverify.testClass4&quot;&lt;/span&gt; /&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;/classes&amp;gt; 
  &amp;lt;/test&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/suite&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Use surefire plugin in pom:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&amp;lt;plugins&amp;gt; 
  &amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;maven-compiler-plugin&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;version&amp;gt;3.7.0&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt; &amp;lt;source&amp;gt;1.8&amp;lt;/source&amp;gt; &amp;lt;target&amp;gt;1.8&amp;lt;/target&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;      
  &amp;lt;/plugin&amp;gt;
  &amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;maven-surefire-plugin&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;version&amp;gt;3.0.0-M4&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt; 
    &amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt; 
      &amp;lt;suiteXmlFiles&amp;gt; &amp;lt;file&amp;gt;src/test/resources/ts1234.xml&amp;lt;/file&amp;gt; &amp;lt;/suiteXmlFiles&amp;gt;   
    &amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt; 
   &amp;lt;/plugin&amp;gt;
 &amp;lt;/plugins&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Run above project:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mvn clean install&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;INFO&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; -------------------------------------------------------&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;INFO&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; T E S T S&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;INFO&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; -------------------------------------------------------&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;INFO&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Running TestSuite&lt;br/&gt;
 class1method1&lt;br/&gt;
 class2method1&lt;br/&gt;
 class3method1&lt;br/&gt;
 class4method1&lt;br/&gt;
 class2method1 end&lt;br/&gt;
 class3method1 end&lt;br/&gt;
 class4method1 end&lt;br/&gt;
 class1method1 end&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;INFO&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Tests run: 4, Failures: 0, Errors: 0, Skipped: 0, Time elapsed: 1.617 s - in TestSuite&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But in ${project}/target/surefire-reports/testng-results.xml, only 3 cases were found. Also under ${project}/target/surefire-reports/junitreports folder, only 3 files were generated.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In general, if the thread-count &amp;gt; 1, it happens randomly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Centos 7 +JDK 1.8.0 + Maven 3.0.5 + surefire plugin 2.19.1 + testng 6.8;&lt;br/&gt;
Centos 7 + JDK 1.8.0 + Maven 3.5.2 + surefire plugin 2.19.1 + testng 6.8;&lt;br/&gt;
Windows 10 + JDK 1.8.0 + Maven 3.5.0 + surefirel plugin 3.0.0-M4 + testng 6.8;&lt;br/&gt;
